_header: Freshest of colour and most amiable
_description: A plea to his mistress — a roundel

CamTCC600.First Lines:
ffresshest of colour and moste amyableConsider þe my peyne and
                    beoþe merciable…
CamTCC600.Last Lines:
…þane letteþe þis compleynt in your hert
                    synkSuffre þe not my trouþe to eoude þus
                    gerdonlesse
